      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="f76ec0063049d943" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: Halflings are remarkably skilled with knives, clubs, slings, and small bows. They prefer not to fight larger creatures head on; instead they stay at range, plan ambushes to quickly overwhelm opponents, or team up with a larger ally so they can attack a foe’s back and legs.</source>
