      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="e8d042cee7421c92" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Interaction: Halflings enjoy the company of larger folks as long as they aren’t mocked for their size. They’re brave and determined when they need to be, though some might complain about wanting to go home.</source>
